{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2017}} {{Infobox person | name = Achuth Mohandas | image = | image_size = 260x260px | caption = Achuth Mohanas at International Film Festival of Kerala (IFFK) | birth_date = {{Birth date|df=yes|1988|5|16}} | birth_place = [[Trivandrum]], India | nationality = Indian | citizenship = India | occupation =writer, actor, [[radio jockey]] |notable_works = {{Plainlist}} * ''Ormmayilliniyee Mukham'' * ''Sorry, I'm Taken'' * ''Money Back Policy'' {{Endplainlist}} }}
'''Achuth Mohandas''' is an Indian-born writer who writes in both English and Malayalam. He was a [[radio jockey]] (RJ) with Red FM 93.5, which is a leading radio broadcasting brand in India, from 2008 to 2013. He is a graduate in Physics and started his career in the entertainment industry when he was just 19 years old while pursuing his final year degree course.
== Early life == Achuth Mohandas (born Achuth B.) was born on 16, May 1988 in Trivandrum, India. He finished his schooling from [[Government Model Boys Higher Secondary School]] and Salvation Army Higher Secondary School. He secured his graduation in Physics from [[Mahatma Gandhi College]] under [[University of Kerala]] in the year 2008.
== Career == In 2008, he joined [[Red FM 93.5]] as a [[Radio personality|Radio Jockey]] and continued his employment till 2013.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.yentha.com/news/view/4/my-iffk-2014-film-festival-expectations-achuth-mohandas|title=My IFFK 2014: Film Festival Expectations – Trivandrum News {{!}} Yentha.com|last=yentha.com|website=www.yentha.com|language=en|access-date=2017-05-29}}</ref> After those five years of employment, he started dedicating most of his time towards other areas of media like writing, publishing, media production and other streams of entertainment Industry.
He was also a [[VJ (media personality)|video jockey]] (VJ) with [[JaiHind TV|Jai Hind TV]], [[SS Music|SS Entertainment]] Channel, Today TV, [[Asianet News]], etc. and hosted several TV shows for them. After spending many years in the broadcasting media, he is now a conceptualises of advertisements and handles the promotion of various brands.
Achuth has also acted in different movies and a number of short movies too. Currently, he is dedicating most of his time to writing.
