'''Varisi''' is an [[indigenous language]] of [[Choiseul Province]], [[Solomon Islands]].
== External links == * [[Paradisec]] has [http://catalog.paradisec.org.au/collections/search?language_code=vrs a number of collections that include Varisi language materials.]
